# 📺 YouTube Clone (React + Material UI + Axios)

A responsive YouTube clone built using **React**, **Material UI**, and **Axios**. This project replicates core YouTube features such as video browsing, searching, and playback using a clean modern UI and external API integration.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔍 Search videos by keyword  
- 📺 Watch video playback screen  
- 📃 Display video details (title, channel, views, etc.)  
- 📱 Fully responsive UI for all devices  
- 🎨 Styled using Material UI (MUI)  
- 🌐 Data fetching using Axios  
- ⚡ Fast and dynamic user experience  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- React.js – Frontend library  
- Material UI – UI framework  
- Axios – HTTP client  
- YouTube Data API v3 – Video data source  

---

